          <p><strong>Organic Search</strong> Organic search refers to the unpaid, algorithm-driven listings that appear in search engine results pages. Unlike paid ads, organic results are earned.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="term-meta-strip">
          <div class="tms-cell">
            <div class="tms-label">Category</div>
            <div class="tms-value">SEO</div>
          </div>
